  "content": "<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 700 500\" font-family=\"'JetBrains Mono', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">VDM Layer Architecture</text>\n\n  <!-- Layer 4: Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"150\" y=\"50\" width=\"400\" height=\"70\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"75\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Consumption View</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"95\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#166534\">Fiori UI / OData service exposure</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"110\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">UI annotations, @Search, @Consumption.*</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"350\" y1=\"120\" x2=\"350\" y2=\"145\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Layer 3: Composite -->\n  <rect x=\"150\" y=\"150\" width=\"400\" height=\"70\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Composite View</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#854D0E\">Business logic, joins, calculations</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">Associations, aggregations, currency conversion</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"350\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"350\" y2=\"245\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Layer 2: Basic -->\n  <rect x=\"150\" y=\"250\" width=\"400\" height=\"70\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">Basic / Interface View</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#991B1B\">Reusable data foundation</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">Field selection, alias, simple filter logic</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"350\" y1=\"320\" x2=\"350\" y2=\"345\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n\n  <!-- Layer 1: Private -->\n  <rect x=\"150\" y=\"350\" width=\"400\" height=\"70\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Private View</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#581C87\">Internal abstraction, hidden from consumers</text>\n  <text x=\"350\" y=\"410\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">Complex joins, technical mapping, no annotations</text>\n\n  <!-- DB Source arrows -->\n  <line x1=\"150\" y1=\"385\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"385\" stroke=\"#94A3B8\" stroke-width=\"1\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  <text x=\"115\" y=\"378\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748b\">SELECT</text>\n  <text x=\"115\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748b\">from</text>\n\n  <rect x=\"20\" y=\"360\" width=\"60\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"385\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\">DB</text>\n  <text x=\"50\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">Tables</text>\n\n  <!-- Side label -->\n  <text x=\"570\" y=\"76\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">👤 Fiori / API</text>\n  <text x=\"570\" y=\"176\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">🧩 Business Logic</text>\n  <text x=\"570\" y=\"276\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">📐 Reusable</text>\n  <text x=\"570\" y=\"376\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">🔒 Internal</text>\n</svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_VDMBAS'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - VDM Basic (Interface) View Type'\n@VDM.viewType: #BASIC\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION\n@ObjectModel.dataType: #BASIC\n@OData.publish: true\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC\n  as select from ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE\n{\n  key TravelId,\n      AgencyId,\n      CustomerId,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      BookingFee,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      TotalPrice,\n      CurrencyCode,\n      Description,\n      Status,\n      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true\n      Createdby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      Createdat,\n      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true\n      Lastchangedby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      Lastchangedat\n}</code></pre>",
